/******************************************************************************                      
** Name:     sp_dsNextDayInSet                      
** Short Desc: Date calculation utility proc
**                      
** Full Description: Date calculation utility proc. Resets date to the next day which falls on or after @seed_date and 
which falls on a day indicated in @day_set.  
**                              
** Input Arguments:   
